{
  "name": "Trendline",
  "summary": "<p>趋势线显示系列中数据的趋势或方向。<strong>Trendline</strong> 对象是 <strong>Trendlines</strong> 集合的成员。<strong>Trendlines</strong> 集合包含某一个系列的所有 <strong>Trendline</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>Trendlines</strong>(<em>index</em>)（其中 <em>index</em>是趋势线索引号）可返回一个 <strong>Trendline</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p>索引号指出趋势线添加到系列中的顺序。<code>Trendlines(1)</code> 是第一个添加到系列中的趋势线，而 <code>Trendlines(Trendlines.Count)</code> 是最后一个。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例更改工作表一上嵌入式图表一中第一个系列的趋势线类型。如果该系列没有趋势线，则本示例会失败。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlMovingAvg\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除 Chart1 中第三个数据系列索引为2的趋势线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    series.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表图表上的趋势线。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<p>本示例显示一条有关创建 <code>myObject</code>的应用程序的消息。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Backward2",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置趋势线向后延伸的周期数目（或散点图中的单位个数）。可读/写 <strong>Double</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例对 Chart1 中的趋势线向前和向后延伸的单位数进行设置。本示例应在包含具有趋势线的单个序列的 2D 柱形图上运行*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> trendline = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    trendline.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Forward2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n    trendline.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Backward2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示第一张工作表上的第一个图表的第二个数据系列索引为2的趋势线向后延伸的单位数。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(series2.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Backward2</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（double 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Border",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Border</strong>对象，它代表对象的边框。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例更改 Chart1 中的第三个数据系列索引为1的趋势线线型*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> trendline = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    trendline.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineStyle</span> = xlDash\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示第一张工作表上的第一个图表的第一个数据系列索引为2的趋势线边框粗细是否为细线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series1 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(series1.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> == xlHairline)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Border",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "DataLabel",
      "summary": "<p>若要打开趋势线的数据标签，需要将 <strong>DisplayEquation</strong> 属性和 <strong>DisplayRSquared</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>True</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>DataLabel</strong>对象，它代表与趋势线相关的数据标签。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例为 Chart1 中的第一个数据系列索引为1的趋势线启用数据标签，并显示数据标签文本方向是否为水平排列*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> trendline = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    trendline.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayRSquared</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    trendline.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayEquation</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(trendline.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataLabel</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Orientation</span> == xlHorizontal)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例为第一张工作表上的第一个图表的第二个数据系列索引为2的趋势线启用数据标签，并选中数据标签。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    series.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayRSquared</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    series.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayEquation</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    series.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataLabel</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "DataLabel",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "DisplayEquation",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果显示图表中的趋势线公式，则该值为 <strong>True</strong>（其数据标签与 R-平方值相同）。将该属性设为 <strong>True</strong> 可自动显示数据标签。<strong>Boolean</strong>类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示 Chart1 上趋势线 1 的 R 平方值和公式。本示例应在具有第一个系列趋势线的 2D 柱形图上运行。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> trendline = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    trendline.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayRSquared</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    trendline.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayEquation</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示第一张工作表上的第一个图表的第三个数据系列索引为1的趋势线公式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series3 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    series3.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayEquation</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "DisplayRSquared",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果显示图表中趋势线的 R-平方值，则该值为 <strong>True</strong>（其数据标签与公式的相同）。将该属性设为 <strong>True</strong> 可自动显示数据标签。<strong>Boolean</strong>类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示 Chart1 上趋势线 1 的 R 平方值和公式。本示例应在具有第一个系列趋势线的 2D 柱形图上运行。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> trendline = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    trendline.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayRSquared</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    trendline.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayEquation</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示第一张工作表上的第一个图表的第二个数据系列索引为2的趋势线的 R 平方值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    series2.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayRSquared</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Format",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回 <strong>ChartFormat</strong>对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例更改 Chart1 中的第二个数据系列索引为1的趋势线的虚线样式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> trendline = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    trendline.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DashStyle</span> = msoLineLongDash\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置第一张工作表上的第一个图表的第一个数据系列索引为2的趋势线发光半径为2。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    series.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Glow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Radius</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "ChartFormat",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Forward2",
